itemdescription: Steel bracket, 150mm, galvanized finish for structural support.
Hex bolt, M8 x 40mm, zinc-plated, used in mechanical assemblies.
M8 lock nut, nylon insert, corrosion-resistant, vibration-proof.
Flat washer, M8, stainless steel, for load distribution.
Plastic gear, 20 teeth, injection molded, Nylon 66.
Assembled PCB with microcontroller, version 3.0, RoHS compliant.
4-core control cable, 1 meter, PVC insulated, industrial use.
DC motor, 12V, 10W, with leads and mounting holes.
NTC thermistor temperature sensor, 10K?, epoxy coated.
Aluminum heatsink, 50x50mm, with fins for passive cooling.
H-Bridge motor driver, dual channel, 12-24V compatible.
Polyurethane tubing, 8mm OD, flexible, abrasion-resistant.
Deep groove ball bearing, 608ZZ, shielded, pre-lubricated.
Aluminum base plate, 5mm thick, drilled and tapped.
ABS plastic enclosure, 120x90x50mm, snap-fit cover.
